msgid "ghānañca paṭicca gandhe ca uppajjati ghānaviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā vedanā; "
msgstr "Nose consciousness arises dependent on the nose and smells. The meeting of the three is contact. Contact is a condition for feeling. "

msgctxt "mn148:8.6"
msgid "jivhañca paṭicca rase ca uppajjati jivhāviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā vedanā; "
msgstr "Tongue consciousness arises dependent on the tongue and tastes. The meeting of the three is contact. Contact is a condition for feeling. "

