msgstr "‘The six classes of feeling should be understood.’ "

msgctxt "mn148:8.10"
msgid "iti yaṃ taṃ vuttaṃ, idametaṃ paṭicca vuttaṃ. "
msgstr "That’s what I said, and this is why I said it. "

msgctxt "mn148:8.11"
msgid "Idaṃ pañcamaṃ chakkaṃ. (5) "
msgstr "This is the fifth set of six. "

