msgid "Cakkhuñca paṭicca rūpe ca uppajjati cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, tiṇṇaṃ saṅgati phasso, phassapaccayā vedanā, vedanāpaccayā taṇhā; "
msgstr "Eye consciousness arises dependent on the eye and sights. The meeting of the three is contact. Contact is a condition for feeling. Feeling is a condition for craving. "

msgctxt "mn148:9.4"
msgid "sotañca paṭicca sadde ca uppajjati sotaviññāṇaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Ear consciousness … "

msgctxt "mn148:9.5"
msgid "ghānañca paṭicca gandhe ca uppajjati ghānaviññāṇaṃ … "
msgstr "Nose consciousness … "

msgctxt "mn148:9.6"
msgid "jivhañca paṭicca rase ca uppajjati jivhāviññāṇaṃ … "
