msgid "Yassa kho pana uppādopi vayopi paññāyati, ‘attā me uppajjati ca veti cā’ti iccassa evamāgataṃ hoti. "
msgstr "so it would follow that one’s self arises and vanishes. "

msgctxt "mn148:10.10"
msgid "Tasmā taṃ na upapajjati: "
msgstr "That’s why it’s not tenable to claim that "

msgctxt "mn148:10.11"
msgid "‘rūpā attā’ti yo vadeyya. "
msgstr "sights are self. "

msgctxt "mn148:10.12"
msgid "Iti cakkhu anattā, rūpā anattā. "
msgstr "So the eye is not self and sights are not self. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "mn148:10.13"
msgid "‘Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ attā’ti yo vadeyya taṃ na upapajjati. "
msgstr "If anyone says, ‘eye consciousness is self,’ that is not tenable. "

