msgctxt "mn148:41.2"
msgid "ghānasmiṃ nibbindati, gandhesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "nose … "

msgctxt "mn148:41.3"
msgid "jivhāya nibbindati, rasesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "tongue … "

msgctxt "mn148:41.4"
msgid "kāyasmiṃ nibbindati, phoṭṭhabbesu nibbindati … "
msgstr "body … "

msgctxt "mn148:41.5"
msgid "manasmiṃ nibbindati, dhammesu nibbindati, manoviññāṇe nibbindati, manosamphasse nibbindati, vedanāya nibbindati, taṇhāya nibbindati. "
msgstr "mind, thoughts, mind consciousness, mind contact, feeling, and craving. "

msgctxt "mn148:41.6"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati, virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When it is freed, they know it is freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn148:41.7"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc32
msgctxt "mn148:41.8"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn148:41.9"
msgid "Attamanā te bhikkhū bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandunti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, the mendicants were happy with what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn148:41.10"
msgid "Imasmiṃ kho pana veyyākaraṇasmiṃ bhaññamāne saṭṭhimattānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ anupādāya āsavehi cittāni vimucciṃsūti. "
msgstr "And while this discourse was being spoken, the minds of sixty mendicants were freed from defilements by not grasping. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn148:41.11"
msgid "Chachakkasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

